12", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75608434_3888160121466645_4102924857382221306_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rEhrBlVxJdoQ7kNvgFCtLhg&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ARX_yvb_A_mdc_P79YpU5bE&oh=00_AYC41-LE8BjKwo0zD4Sh1eCF0dRrOHp1NzN_zA7PJZwUag&oe=66F3E53C"}, {"file_name": "38974771_914663160423989_8412528913888708301_n.png", "id": "1471442040147115", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003240_1471442043480448_4137664387287025678_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=be_O0yc8p44Q7kNvgGxNdoy&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ARX_yvb_A_mdc_P79YpU5bE&oh=00_AYBJOMU6wp5UANmMqxb_Tu9uMkiAocidV82D_9-OJRDgsg&oe=66F3E996"}, {"file_name": "57568678_442736708598857_2601426099645306453_n.png", "id": "1585260168698302", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569443_1585260175364968_5377620633503669556_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pSgJrOXgKPUQ7kNvgFePfcy&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ARX_yvb_A_mdc_P79YpU5bE&oh=00_AYDlJGJrNQ5-ODXHtB-62oMM_8cHHX6pHlS8zmChB3BzvA&oe=66F3DC78"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Simtryx", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Experience the next step in virtual simulations for healthcare**\n\nTalk, observe, and interact with your patient to diagnose them correctly inside the most immersive and accessible simulation for VR headsets.\n\nImmerse yourself with our powerful main features:\n\n- **AI-powered speech simulation**: Talk freely with the patient to learn more about their history, habits, and to empathize with them.\n- **Advanced hand tracking**: Built from the ground up with hand tracking in mind, every object in the world has a physical presence, and your virtual hands won't phase through.\n- **Seamless onboarding**: Through video passthrough, bring 3D elements into your physical space and jump into the simulation in the most comfortable way.\n\nWith our focus on accessibility, ease 